articles.author: Staff Writer
articles.title: KMT picks upstart Cheng Li-wun as new leader, jolting Taiwan's old guard - Nikkei Asia
articles.description: 55-year-old is second woman to be elected chief in opposition party's history
articles.content: TAIPEI -- Taiwan's opposition Kuomintang on Saturday elected Cheng Li-wun as its next leader, picking an upstart over an old-guard favorite and sending a shock through the political class.
